title: Safet Alic
text:
Safet Alic (born 4 February 1999) is a Swiss <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> of Bosnia and Herzegovina origin who plays for <a href="FC%20Biel-Bienne">Biel-Bienne</a>.
Club career.
Alic made his professional debut for <a href="Neuch%C3%A2tel%20Xamax">Neuchâtel Xamax</a> in a 3-0 <a href="Swiss%20Super%20League">Swiss Super League</a> loss to <a href="FC%20Basel">FC Basel</a> on 24 August 2019. He joined <a href="Yverdon%20Sport%20FC">Yverdon Sport</a> in August 2020.
